    <string name="app_name">Offline CDR Analyzer</string>
    <string name="about_title">About Me &amp; App Capabilities</string>
    <string name="about_capabilities"><![CDATA[
        • <b>Multi-Party Link Correlation:</b> Identifies common contacts called by at least two different suspects.<br/>
        • <b>Interactive 3D Visualization:</b> Renders relationship links and hardware signatures in a dynamic 3D space.<br/>
        • <b>Advanced Hardware Forensics:</b> Detects IMEI swapping (hopping) and multi-SIM handset sharing patterns.<br/>
        • <b>Geospatial Pattern Analysis:</b> Profiles movement clusters, frequent night-stay towers, and tower text similarity.<br/>
        • <b>Temporal Intelligence:</b> Calculates "Critical Window" activity (01:00 AM - 04:00 AM) against total night operations.<br/>
        • <b>Background Optimization:</b> Silent pre-processing of movement correlation for instant results.<br/>
        • <b>Unified Intelligence Export:</b> Generates consolidated Excel and PDF reports with automated formatting.<br/>
        • <b>Local Edge Processing:</b> All analysis is done 100% offline on-device to ensure maximum data privacy.
    ]]></string>
